data.description: This West End Station town-home has a spacious layout and modern features, this property is sure to impress. Step inside and be greeted by the hall tree greets you, providing a functional and organized space to hang coats and store shoes. You'll notice stylish interior and beautiful plank flooring, featuring granite countertops + subway tile backsplash adds a trendy flair to the space, making it a joy to entertain guests. The master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with an accent wall that adds a pop of color and personality. You'll find a convenient walk-in closet, providing ample storage space for all your belongings. Also upstairs, you'll find 2 additional bedrooms + a versatile loft area, perfect for a home office, playroom, or additional living space. No more hauling laundry up and down the stairs, as the laundry room is conveniently located on the second level. Located near downtown Lebanon, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options!
